data.name: richTextBox1.Text
data.value: Access Rights Full Access - Allows a user to open the mailbox and behave as its owner Send As - Allows a user to send an email from the mailbox as the mailbox sender Send On Behalf - Will indicate that the message was sent by the user on behalf of the owner Forwarding - Emails sent to the specific mailbox are being forwarded to the user/group Group Member - User is a member of the specific group/distribution list Mailbox Forwarding To Group - Mailbox forwarding to Distribution List or Security Group displays Members of the Group
